trans-unit.source: Represents the resolution supported by a printer.
trans-unit.target: 表示支持打印机的分辨率。

trans-unit.source: This class is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties to get the printer resolutions that are available on the printer and to set the printing resolution for a page, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 此类由<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>和<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName>属性以获取位于打印机的打印机分辨率并分别设置页，打印的分辨率。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PageSettings.PrinterResolution%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterSettings.PrinterResolutions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> property to determine whether the printer resolution type is the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> value <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: 使用<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>属性来确定打印机解决方法类型是否为<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>值<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>

trans-unit.source: If so, use the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A> and <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> properties to determine the printer resolution in the horizontal and vertical directions, respectively.
trans-unit.target: 如果是，使用<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>和<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A>属性，以分别确定沿水平方向和垂直方向，打印机解决方法。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Y%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.X%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information on printing, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace overview.
trans-unit.target: 有关打印的详细信息，请参阅<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空间概述。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Gets the horizontal printer resolution, in dots per inch.
trans-unit.target: 获取水平打印机的分辨率，以每英寸点数。

trans-unit.source: `dmPrintQuality` is a member of the `DEVMODE` (device mode) structure, which defines constants that map to printer quality settings.
trans-unit.target: `dmPrintQuality`为属于`DEVMODE`（设备模式） 结构，它定义映射到打印机质量设置的常量。

trans-unit.source: The X property contains the value `DMRES_HIGH` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_MEDIUM` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, `DMRES_LOW` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>, and `DMRES_DRAFT` if <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>.
trans-unit.target: X 属性包含值`DMRES_HIGH`如果<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>设置为<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>，`DMRES_MEDIUM`如果<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>设置为<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>，`DMRES_LOW`如果<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>设置为<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>，和`DMRES_DRAFT`如果<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>设置为<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind>。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolutionKind> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrinterResolution.Kind%2A>
